ta-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/public_services/frequently_asked_questions/driving_test/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"94063754114ab78f26504d1658c30044b011bf43","tid":1644263,"uid":36638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"搭單問<br />\n如果乙部合格丙部肥左<br />\n想轉車種 係咪都要由筆試從頭黎過"}]}